These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: dancing, drawing, photography
The people have 3 different jobs:  manager, bartender, security-guard
1. the security-guard is somewhere between the person who's hobby is dancing and the bartender##7
2. the manager is somewhere to the right of the bartender##5
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the right of the bartender##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3   |
| Hobby   | photography | drawing | dancing |
| Job           | bartender  | security-guard     | manager  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-2::.
3 different games are played: go, snooker, scrabble
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, scientist, nurse
1. the journalist is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing go is somewhere between the person playing scrabble and the scientist##7
3. the journalist is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |
| Game   | snooker | go | scrabble |
| Job     | scientist       | nurse     | journalist |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  manager, software-developer, engineer
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, fishing, rock-climbing
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere between the manager and the person who's hobby is reading##7
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the software-developer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |   3    |
| Job    | manager | software-developer | engineer  |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing  | fishing  | reading |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-4::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, pall-mall, bolivar
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, taxi, car
1. the game-smoker is somewhere between the person driving the car and the pall-mall-smoker##7
2. the person driving the taxi is not the game-smoker##6
3. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |      3      |
| Cigar           | pall-mall | game | bolivar     |
| Transport   | taxi    | skateboard          | car |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-5::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, light-blue, brown
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, june, january
1. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who likes light-blue##7
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
3. the person who likes light-blue is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Color   | purple      | brown     | light-blue   |
| Birthday     | january | june | march |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-6::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, mauve, pink
There 3 different types of food: cucumber, cherry, peas
1. the person eating cucumber is on the left or right of the person eating cherry##3
2. the person eating cherry is somewhere to the left of the person eating cucumber##5
3. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person eating peas##1
4. the person who likes mauve is somewhere between the person eating peas and the person who likes ebony##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Color   | pink    | mauve     | ebony     |
| Food   | peas | cherry | cucumber |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-7::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, train, tram
There are 3 different favourite colors: turquise, green, red
1. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
2. the person who likes red is somewhere between the person driving the taxi and the person who likes turquise##7
3. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Transport     | tram       | train      | taxi       |
| Color   | turquise | red | green |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-8::.
3 different pets are kept: cat, rat, turtle
3 different games are played: whist, canasta, backgammon
1. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
2. the person playing whist is somewhere between the person playing backgammon and the owner of the rat##7
3. the person playing canasta is on the right of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Pet           | turtle | cat  | rat |
| Game   | backgammon      | whist | canasta      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-9::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, mirinda
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, april, january
1. the person who's birthday is in january is not the person drinking mirinda##6
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in april and the person drinking coffee##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | coffee | mirinda | 7up   |
| Birthday     | january    | august  | april |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-10::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, dubstep, r&b
3 different pets are kept: fish, ferret, chinchilla
1. the fan techno is on the right of the fan r&b##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is the fan dubstep##1
3. the fan r&b is somewhere between the fan dubstep and the owner of the ferret##7

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep   | r&b    | techno |
| Pet      | chinchilla | fish | ferret |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-11::.
House: colonial, gothic-revival, farmhouse
City: boston, san-francisco, marseilles
1. the colonial house is somewhere between the person traveling to san-francisco and the person traveling to boston##7
2. the colonial house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
3. the person traveling to boston is not the farmhouse house##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| House         | farmhouse | colonial | gothic-revival |
| City   | san-francisco    | marseilles    | boston         |

