.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-12::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rowing, cycling
The people have 3 different hobbies: dancing, magic-tricks, filmmaking
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##7
3. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| Sport          | ice-hockey  | cycling       | rowing     |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | dancing | magic-tricks |

