.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-13::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, adventure, martial-arts
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, quad-bike, boat
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere between the person driving the snowmobile and the person driving the boat##7
2. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere between the person driving the snowmobile and the person watching adventure movies##7
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |  3   |
| Movie-Genre      | satire     | martial-arts | adventure |
| Transport   | snowmobile | quad-bike    | boat |

