.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-20::.
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, papaya, cranberry
House: modern, colonial, victorian
1. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the modern house##1
2. the person eating cranberry is somewhere between the person eating papaya and the colonial house##7
3. the person eating cranberry is somewhere to the left of the colonial house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Food   | papaya      | cranberry     | pomegranate |
| House        | victorian | modern | colonial    |

 